## MacHelper Pro

- Enables the live MacHelper Pro Lemon Squeezy checkout flow in the app.
- Enables Buy License links on the MacHelper Pro website in all supported languages.
- Keeps MacHelper Pro license validation tied to the MacHelper Pro Lemon Squeezy product and variant.

]]></description>
