            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[
## MacHelper Pro

- Improved the Auto Wi-Fi Switch location-permission flow so the permission prompt appears when the feature is enabled and the menu refreshes after approval.
- Improved launch coordination across the HelperSuite family so only one HelperSuite app is active at a time.
- Refined Finder context menus and open actions, including selected-path handoff to editor, terminal, Codex, VSCode, and custom app handlers.
- Added product-specific website/privacy routing for the MacHelper family.
- Improved release automation so build numbers, appcasts, websites, and latest build artifacts stay in sync.

]]></description>
