        <item>
            <title>1.0.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 05:24:15 -0700</pubDate>
            <link>https://xintechllc.com/MacHelperPro/</link>
            <sparkle:version>15</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (15)

- Keeps only one HelperSuite family app running at a time to avoid overlapping
  menu bar behavior across DisplayHelper, DisplayHelper Pro, MacHelper, and
  MacHelper Pro.
- Ensures Finder context menus are owned by the active HelperSuite app, so
  multiple installed Finder extensions do not show duplicate actions.
- Uses the direct MacHelper Pro Finder extension when no family app is running
  and both MacHelper variants are installed.
- Refreshes DMG packaging so Sparkle's bundled updater helpers are signed with
  secure Developer ID timestamps before notarization.
]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/Samx2015/MacHelperPro/releases/download/v1.0.0/MacHelperPro-1.0.0-15-macOS.dmg" length="5370789" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="cbkeFiykY4kuwulFH0fwLEWw7a2oaVRDARYUTgULdmCAFyysEW7KhtLO1/oxwXUwZKQfk7bDaKBTtiYUi1qZCA=="/>
        </item>
